# 🛠️ Tools for Password Strength Evaluation

## Online Checkers Used
- **PasswordMeter**: https://www.passwordmeter.com/
- **Kaspersky Password Checker**: https://password.kaspersky.com/
- **NordPass Strength Checker**: https://nordpass.com/password-strength-checker/

Each tool provides a score or grade for passwords based on:
- Length
- Character variety
- Use of dictionary words
- Predictability
